==English==
===Noun===
'''[[boiled]] [[egg]]''' (''plural:'' '''boiled eggs''')

# An [[egg]] of a [[domestic]] [[fowl]], normally of a [[chicken]], [[cook]]ed in its [[shell]] in [[simmer]]ing [[water]].

